End users redistributing this software should review the licenses of bundled
third-party components before commercial use. PySide6 ships under LGPL v3,
which permits redistribution under MIT (this project's license) provided the
Qt libraries remain dynamically linked and replaceable — both conditions
that are satisfied by the standard PyInstaller bundle produced by
`build_app.sh`.
